### =============================================
###  ЮKASSA PAYMENT API — ТЕСТЫ (VS Code REST Client)
### =============================================
### Инструкция:
### 1. Установи расширение "REST Client" в VS Code
### 2. Замени @token на реальный токен пользователя (api_key из таблицы users)
### 3. После первого запроса /create вставь payment.id в переменную @payment_id
### 4. Нажимай "Send Request" над каждым запросом

@host = https://twelvesteps-backend.onrender.com
@token = {$dotenv TEST_TOKEN}}
@payment_id = {$dotenv YOOKASSA_PAYMENT_ID}}
@bot_nickname = {$dotenv TELEGRAM_BOT_NICKNAME}}

### =============================================
### 1. Создать платёж — Monthly (990 ₽)
### =============================================
POST {{host}}/payment/yookassa/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 990,
  "description": "Подписка GPT-SELF — monthly",
  "plan_type": "monthly",
  "return_url": "https://t.me/{{bot_nickname}}"
}

### =============================================
### 2. Создать платёж — Yearly (2990 ₽)
### =============================================
POST {{host}}/payment/yookassa/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2990,
  "description": "Подписка GPT-SELF — yearly",
  "plan_type": "yearly",
  "return_url": "https://t.me/{{bot_nickname}}"
}

### =============================================
### 3. Создать платёж — 3 месяца (2490 ₽)
### =============================================
POST {{host}}/payment/yookassa/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2490,
  "description": "Подписка GPT-SELF — 3 месяца",
  "plan_type": "3_months",
  "return_url": "https://t.me/{{bot_nickname}}"
}

### =============================================
### 4. Проверить статус платежа
### =============================================
GET {{host}}/payment/yookassa/status/{{payment_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =============================================
### 5. Симуляция Webhook от ЮKassa (для ручного теста)
### =============================================
# POST {{host}}/payment/yookassa/webhook
# Content-Type: application/json
# X-Yookassa-Signature: test-signature-123   # подпись не проверяется в тесте

# {
#   "type": "notification",
#   "event": "payment.succeeded",
#   "object": {
#     "id": "{{payment_id}}",
#     "status": "succeeded",
#     "paid": true,
#     "amount": { "value": "990.00", "currency": "RUB" },
#     "metadata": {
#       "user_id": "123",
#       "plan_type": "monthly"
#     }
#   }
# }

### =============================================
### CRYPTOMUS PAYMENT API — ТЕСТЫ (VS Code REST Client)
### =============================================

### 1. Создать платёж — Monthly (USD)
POST {{host}}/payment/cryptomus/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 9.90,
  "currency": "USD",
  "description": "Подписка GPT-SELF — monthly",
  "plan_type": "monthly",
  "return_url": "https://t.me/{{bot_nickname}}"
}

### 2. Создать платёж — Yearly (BTC/USDT)
POST {{host}}/payment/cryptomus/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 29.90,
  "currency": "USDT",
  "description": "Подписка GPT-SELF — yearly",
  "plan_type": "yearly",
  "return_url": "https://t.me/{{bot_nickname}}"
}

### 3. Проверить статус платежа
GET {{host}}/payment/cryptomus/status/{{payment_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Симуляция Webhook от Cryptomus
# POST {{host}}/payment/cryptomus/webhook
# Sign: test-signature-123
# 
# {
#   "type": "payment",
#   "uuid": "{{payment_id}}",
#   "status": "paid",
#   "amount": "9.90",
#   "currency": "USD",
#   "metadata": {
#     "user_id": "123",
#     "plan_type": "monthly"
#   }
# }

### =============================================
### Полезные советы:
### • Что бы получить @token 
### • Скопируй полный External Database URL
### • Выполни запрос: SELECT api_key FROM users LIMIT 1;
### • После /create скопируй "confirmation_url" из ответа и открой в браузере
### • После оплаты скопируй payment.id и вставь в переменную @payment_id сверху
### • Для реального webhook используй ngrok + тестовый магазин ЮKassa